       Change Summary Explanation
       FY24 adjustments include Congressional Adds of $5M for Battery Replacement and $10M for Data Bus Cybersecurity and several small Congressional Marks
       totaling -$1.880M. Also, $9.484M was reprogrammed from F-22 ($4.485M was payback for the use of FY23 funds, $4.999M was for OFP shortfalls). FY25
