development, test, and user evaluation. This includes, but not limited to PIA, Consortium, SBIR, DLA TLS, TACFI, etc. and may award to multiple vendors.

 The acquisition strategy for the Powered Aerospace Ground Equipment (AGE) Modernization project is expected to maximize OTA non-traditional contracts for
 development, test, and user evaluation. This includes, but not limited to PIA, Consortium, SBIR, DLA TLS, TACFI, etc. and may award to multiple vendors.

 The acquisition strategy for Tow Systems Modernization project is expected to maximize OTA non-traditional contracts for development, test, and user evaluation. This
 includes, but not limited to PIA, Consortium, SBIR, DLA TLS, TACFI, etc. and may award to multiple vendors.




