4th/5th generation aircraft that improve threat detection techniques, incorporate open system architecture, and advance rapid reprogramming capabilities. Funds were
utilized to leverage existing EW pod components and develop a relevant EW system supporting fighter and attack platforms. No funding required in FY26.

